  "id": "PLACE_the_cinderwake",
  "label": "The Cinderwake",
  "description": "The Cinderwake is a broad-beamed sailing ship adapted to Vespera Tertius, its hull sheathed in soot-darkened plating and its seams sealed against ashfall. A lattice of mast stays and cable-bracing anchors the rigging against the planet’s electrostatic gales, with spars banded in iron to resist grit-scour. Lantern housings sit behind thick glass and shuttered cowls, their light reduced to narrow slits against violet storm-glare. The deck is scored by wind-driven cinders and marked with tether rings and low bulwarks designed for hard weather under rift-shadowed skies.",
